cff-version: 1.2.0
title: subclaw
message: >-
  If you use subclaw in academic work, please cite it as below.
  subclaw is a multi-model LLM gateway for Claude Code, Codex CLI,
  Aider, and Cursor that cuts Claude API spend by 60-90% on read-heavy workloads via
  session-pinned multi-key rotation, Anthropic/OpenAI protocol
  translation, and a USD budget circuit breaker.
